#: ../../nat_helpers.rst:9
msgid ""
"NAT (Network Address Translation) helpers, also known as NAT ALGs "
"(Application Layer Gateways), are components in the firewall that assist "
"in translating IP addresses and port numbers embedded within application-"
"layer data packets. NAT helpers are essential in scenarios where network "
"protocols include IP addresses and port information inside the packet "
"payload, making it necessary to modify these details for proper NAT "
"traversal."
